data.description: The closer a dog looks to a wolf, the less physical problems it will have. Pugs and some terriers have breathing problems because of their short nose. Do you think asphyxiation is cute? Do you think chronic obstructive pulmonary disease is fun? What about cystic fibrosis? Do you want it for your child? Then don't buy a dog with inherent breathing problems.

data.title: Ok I no imgur doesn't like opinions or political stuff but this needs to be said. Cute dog at the end.

images.description:
Racism is racism and sexism is sexism.

There is such an us vs them dynamic on the internet.

we are all humans here and we all should respect each other despite our differences
Left and right.
Black and white.
Men and women.

And you can disagree but still respect that person. 
Everyone has a right to an opinion and Everyone has the right to disagree/agree with that opinion.

And you can have a discussion about that opinion.

You can respect a person and still reserve the right to call their opinion fucking terrible.

There are some racist and sexist fucks out there and there's always gonna be we just have to accept that.

We all need to come together as humans and make the world a better place for everyone. 

where fair and equal discussion can be had and opinions can be shared and people can have the right to call that opinion terrible or agree with it or have a good logical discussion.

so please I urge you help make the world a better and kinder place just by being yourself and doing things that make you happy.

Talk to someone with a different opinion look through their perspective and even if you think their opinions crap don't just say that show them your perspective and opinion and come to a more positive outcome without insults or anger.

We all just have to realize that there is another Person on the other side of the screen and they have feelings too.

Do unto others how you wish others do unto you.
